2012-09-07 Release 0.3.0

Changes:
- Switch to installing from a tarball instead of a package
- Add support for CentOS
- Add support for memcached
- Switch to using vhost template provided by puppetlabs/apache

Bugfixes:
- Resolve resource dependency issues
- Adjust syntax for backwards compatibility with Puppet 2.6

